# LMB Insurance Brokers — Cursor Project Rules

## Project
Premium corporate website for LMB Insurance Brokers (composite insurance broking).

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15 App Router, TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS v4 (CSS-based `@theme` in globals.css)
- Framer Motion (page transitions, UI motion)
- GSAP + ScrollTrigger (scroll-driven animations)
- Lenis (smooth scroll)
- React Hook Form + Zod (forms)
- Embla Carousel (carousels)
- Lucide React (icons)

## Design System
- **Theme:** Black + Cyan premium dark mode
- **Primary:** `#000000`, `#050505` (deep-black)
- **Surface:** `#111111` (graphite), `#0d0d0d`, `#141414` (card)
- **Accent:** `#00d4ff` (cyan), `#00e5ff` (cyan-bright)
- **Fonts:** Inter (body), Syne (display headings)
- **Logo:** `/public/assets/logo/lmb-logo-temporary.png` — invert on dark backgrounds

## Content Rules
- NEVER invent business facts, statistics, or achievements
- Use brochure as primary source when available
- Mark missing client content as `(Content Required from Client)`
- No filler, buzzwords, or generic AI marketing copy
- Every sentence must add value

## Code Conventions
- Use `@/` import alias
- Server Components by default; `"use client"` only when needed
- Content lives in `src/lib/content/`
- Reusable UI in `src/components/ui/`
- Section components in `src/components/sections/`
- Page metadata via `createPageMetadata()` helper
- Use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` for class merging
- Prefer `FadeIn` for scroll reveals; GSAP for complex scroll animations

## Animation Guidelines
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion`
- Page transitions via `PageTransition` wrapper in layout
- Lenis smooth scroll in `LenisProvider`
- Hover: subtle cyan illumination, `-translate-y-1` on cards
- Duration: 300–500ms for micro-interactions, 700ms+ for reveals
- Never excessive or childish animation

## File Structure
```
src/
  app/           # Routes (multi-page)
  components/
    layout/      # Header, Footer, PageHero, PageTransition
    motion/      # FadeIn, TextReveal
    providers/   # Lenis, ScrollTrigger
    sections/    # Page sections
    ui/          # Button, Card, Input, etc.
  lib/
    content/     # Navigation, services, company data
    utils.ts
public/
  assets/logo/   # Temporary logo
```

## Pages
Home, About, Services, Business Lines, Reinsurance, Industries, Why LMB, Process, Leadership, Careers, Resources, FAQ, Contact, Privacy, Terms, 404

## Performance
- Use `next/image` for all images
- Lazy-load GSAP and Lenis (dynamic import)
- Target Lighthouse 95+
- Server Components where possible

## Accessibility
- WCAG AA contrast
- Keyboard navigation for nav and FAQ accordion
- Focus-visible cyan outline
- Semantic HTML and ARIA labels on interactive elements
